4. A board of officers, to consist of:

Captain C. H. Grierson, Quartermaster, 10th Cavalry;

Captain G. H. Macdonald, 10th Cavalry;

1st Lieutenant George Vidmer, 10th Cavalry;

will convene at Manzanillo, Cuba, at 10 o'clock A. M.,

February 5, 1901, or as soon thereafter as practicable, to

examine into and report upon the qualifications of Quarter-

master Sergeant Benjamin W. Anderson, 10th Cavalry, for

appointment as Post Quartermaster Sergeant, U. S. Army.
